## Github steps

1. Make changes

2. Save changes

  - Move `Index.html` from `eda_project/` to `eda_project/docs/` (remove previous `Index.html`

3. In Git pane, click on changed files (Mark as “Staged”)

4. Click on ‘Commit’ icon

5. In commit dialogue box, enter message

6. Click ‘Commit’ (After changes have been committed, close
commit box)

7. Click on “Push” icon (green up arrow) to push changes to GitHub
